All the subjects for intercession enumerated in the Rule ol St. Columbanus are found in the Antiphonary ol Bangor with ten additions. The normal structure os these intercessions or ‘Preces ’ or ‘Orationes’ is an anthem or Versicle followed by a short Collect‚ but No. 4 consists oi three anthems without a Collect‚ and in the Nos. 14 ancl 16. two anthems are prefixed to the Collect.
